name: @ionic-native/network
readme: Improve this doc # Network ``` $ ionic cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-network-information $ npm install --save @ionic-native/network ``` ## [Usage Documentation](https://ionicframework.com/docs/native/network/) Plugin Repo: [https://github.com/apache/cordova-plugin-network-information](https://github.com/apache/cordova-plugin-network-information) Requires Cordova plugin: cordova-plugin-network-information. For more info, please see the [Network plugin docs](https://github.com/apache/cordova-plugin-network-information). ## Supported platforms - Amazon Fire OS - Android - Browser - iOS - Windows
